casebody.data:
McCORMICK, Respondent, v. McCORMICK, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by Thomas P. McCormick against John McCormick, Jr.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Order denying defendant’s motion for new trial, appealed from, affirmed, with costs, and judgment ordered for the plaintiff on the verdict. See 22 N. Y. Supp. 1125.
